nodes.text: Dreadnaught-Five, called D-Five for short, was the fifth of six Dreadnaught-class heavy cruisers used on Outbound Flight.
It came directly from the Rendili StarDrive line for use on the project in 27 BBY. Before Outbound Flight's departure, Dreadnaught-Five had a minor fuel leak problem.
After the crash, it was used as the home of the settlers of the Outbound Flight Colony. One of its rooms was the AA-7 Fire Control Room.
